{"tid":2401233,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭稱擁外國國籍之中國公民不獲領事協助 英外交部斥港府做法錯誤","createTime":"2021-02-09T14:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T23:41:26.000Z","uid":239336,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f0815c89063e8f24b80d17bb1f1e32a0e568b3","tid":2401233,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:29:10.000Z","msg":"英國駐港總領事館昨（8日）更新外遊指示，稱獲悉香港不承認雙重國籍，指若擁有中英雙重國籍人士，即使持英國護照入境，也會被視為中國公民，英國政府在此情況下或未能提供領事協助。<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日重申，擁有外國國籍和在外地享居留權的港人，除非他們宣佈放棄或獲批放棄中國國籍，否則在港仍被會視為中國公民，不會享有外國領事保護和領事探訪權利。英國外交部晚上嚴詞反擊，指香港當局撤銷領事可以探訪在囚擁有英籍的中國公民，並拒絕領事向他們提供協助，做法是錯誤，直指這是自1997年起英國領事的權利。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部更呼籲其國際盟友，共同促請香港當局立即恢復他們可接觸其國民。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府突然一夜之間嚴詞否認雙重國籍，本報向獲特區政府「提示」的英領館查詢，指以往曾否向具有英籍的中國公民提供任何領事協助，以及如何看林鄭今日的言論。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">英國外交部嚴詞回應，批評香港當局撤銷領事探訪和協助在囚、擁有英國國籍的中國公民是錯誤，指這是自1997年起英領事一直享有的權利。英國政府與國際盟友共同呼籲，香港當局立即恢復讓他們探訪其國民的安排。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/SW2NYU2YQVD35AQCQY7NWWCMBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FSW2NYU2YQVD35AQCQY7NWWCMBM%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=b0f377e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FSW2NYU2YQVD35AQCQY7NWWCMBM%2F&h=929e5d41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/SW2NYU2YQVD35AQCQY7NWWCMBM/</a>"},{"pid":"a0e7da5b108d87cb87eb55c9fe92e60ee43349e6","tid":2401233,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3970e2b1641c5ba8dfaf1ffad4463f471af6423a","tid":2401233,"uid":231480,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"貴家公子有咩冬瓜豆腐可唔可以去英國領事館？"},{"pid":"fea4be3a7f4cab0f62a8720fd0b5554c8815f657","tid":2401233,"uid":2054,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:32:42.000Z","msg":"英國制裁柒婆未呀"},{"pid":"6d838da9760747a7522fa0ff33203707700b8942","tid":2401233,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c552d2317ab2bc7034c035dc4fc92b11418b42","tid":2401233,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"邵家臻爆料正確"},{"pid":"a61a1a41d4f056809368e0d85a6c1cbd94f48680","tid":2401233,"uid":194298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3970e2b1641c5ba8dfaf1ffad4463f471af6423a","tid":2401233,"uid":231480,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"貴家公子有咩冬瓜豆腐可唔可以去英國領事館？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"就係無左，而家比中共挾住，所以要全香港人陪佢冚家"},{"pid":"39233a459627ec5f389548b22fc69808a9f6465c","tid":2401233,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"其實係隻支那狗比人制裁，無左祖國協助啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地祖國點會聽隻支那狗講？<br />\n<br />\n不過佢點都作都野出嚟昆藍屍廢老，係好事嚟"},{"pid":"35586b5936e864043e50abdcc334b9ad4ae384dd","tid":2401233,"uid":14941,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"中國以前唔敢郁香港人, 因為神秘, 以為好多外國聯繫<br />\n點知一試水溫, 車原來得把口, 咁我用返平時啲招數了~~"},{"pid":"ad295bf13792f01245b8828ddd680795ddb06986","tid":2401233,"uid":37586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:56:18.000Z","msg":"不如白人黑人黃人入境香港就自動成為支那籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b8123224c5df7d4058e14d10f2187327e98615","tid":2401233,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T17:58: